**Key points to ensure colors work:**

1. CSS file must be at `css/style.css` relative to this HTML.
2. `body` class determines the page palette (`patio`, `tech`, `home-decor`).
3. JS script for dark/light toggle included at the bottom.

After using this template, your page **should immediately display the correct colors**.

